changelog=0.5.11: Streams Restic JSON progress without retaining or repeatedly rescanning the full output, preventing Node CPU usage from growing during long backups.<br>0.5.10: Streams known-size Restic objects directly to pCloud with bounded concurrency and cached remote folders, while retaining a safe staged fallback.<br>0.5.9: Adds detailed live Restic progress including phase, speed, ETA, current files, and errors.<br>0.5.8: Adds encrypted Restic repositories, retention, integrity checks, snapshot browsing, downloads, ZIP export, and isolated restore.<br>0.4.9: Fixes task card status when a long scan has already uploaded every file but the queue still reports the active task.
